--Encrypt--
The file then should be opened and encrypted using the an encryption algorithm.
The encrypted version of the file should then be written back to disk, replacing the contents of the file w/ the “encrypted” contents
When complete the menu should be presented
When viewed, the contents of the file should not be recognizable



--Decrypt--

The file should opened and decrypted using the “reverse” of your encryption algorithm
The un-encrypted version of the file should be written back to disk, replacing the contents of the file with the un-encrypted contents
When complete the menu should be presented
When viewed, the file should look like the original file

